http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/Singareni-Animuthyalu/article14025995.ece

There was an overwhelming response to the job mela conducted by the Singareni Collieries Company Limited in the Ramagundam-3 region under the ‘Singareni Animuthyalu’ in Karimnagar district on Thursday. During the two-day programme, a total of 1150 youth have applied for posts various private sector firms. The participating firms selected 450 candidates and issued employment offer letters.RG-3 general manager MS Venkataramayya, nodal officer P Kondaiah, AGM YGK Murthy and others were also present.